  m_Name: ScenarioData-4
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ScenarioText: 'A New Coworker

    Four years have passed.

    Artificial intelligence
    has become part of everyday life. People no longer use AI only as software, they
    talk to it, ask it questions, and rely on it to help with daily tasks.


    The
    technology feels more natural than ever.


    This morning, Alice contacted
    you before your shift.

    She said the company had deployed a new system to
    every employee.

    You''re about to see what everyone has been talking about.'
